{"tid":1900244,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"身邊有冇啲齋講唔做既廢西","createTime":"2020-02-27T06:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T06:34:09.000Z","uid":90802,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31b29422d89055657ca973a2d167f38ed1dd891d","tid":1900244,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"利申: 非分化撚 <br />\n差唔多次次遊行集會都有出, 甚至隔籬區開花都有去, <br />\n但身邊有啲聲稱黃絲既, 一次集會蒲頭都冇, 仲緒多借口<br />\n去遊行-&gt; 熱<br />\n去集會-&gt; 攰<br />\n去貼連儂牆-&gt;人地有design架咪亂搞啦<br />\n周街貼文宣-&gt; 會比人打<br />\nTwitter國際戰線-&gt; 我得1個twitter acc<br />\n睇直播-&gt; 全部一樣架啦有咩好睇<br />\n罷黨鐵-&gt; 巴士小巴會暈車<br />\n叫佢做乜都有借口話唔去, 最撚叻係食黃店同睇白兵<br />\nfbig日日批評成個運動既做法<br />\n又功能組別 又票投黃區議員 又屌鳩陳雲 連絕對中立既報章都屌埋<br />\n次次出街懶熟政治咁屌周圍屌 <br />\n話佢錯既時候就話唔想講呢個topic<br />\n文宣都搵埋比佢都話唔貼<br />\n呢類人唔該唔好再自稱黃絲, 你係自撚私呀<br />\n<br />\n係呀唔割蓆呀 但害群之馬要屌醒, 咪撚比佢地覺得fb屌兩句就深黃"},{"pid":"e313b6f3b331c96583af0ce2ae6dbb3c745d3c50","tid":1900244,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"遊行集會都拎黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿叔我日日摺紙鶴唱歌添呀柒頭"},{"pid":"eb25fb310cc7668ffdeeef811b552837e6d7c126","tid":1900244,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:18:16.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"244cdd3f8741bc0ac11c3f6219ea321bdf54949c","tid":1900244,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e313b6f3b331c96583af0ce2ae6dbb3c745d3c50","tid":1900244,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"遊行集會都拎黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿叔我日日摺紙鶴唱歌添呀柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:20:42.000Z","msg"